&lt;p>Siehe Release Notes Dovecot: &lt;a href="https://github.com/dovecot/core/blob/release-2.3.21/NEWS"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/dovecot/core/blob/release-2.3.21/NEWS&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
